content: The AI's now grooving to the city beat, but it's picking up too much static. Back to the lab for some fine-tuning. The hustle never stops.

Had a bit of a lightbulb moment today. Our AI can now predict how city life changes with the seasons might affect those niche market trends we've been tracking. Feels like we're on the cusp of something huge, just need to beef up the data collection. This is getting exciting!
